Include Html
    Definition:
     - We can include our html code in our .php file. So we can define templates
       using html elements in external files and include in .php file
     - This helps us to break down our app
    
    include or require keyword:
     - We use this keyword to include all code of external html
     - use either include or require will have the same effect

-- php file 

<body>

    <?php include "header.html"?>
    <p>Hello world</p>
    <?php include "footer.html" ?>

</body>